title: Enji performs "Taivshral" Live on KEXP Trans Musicales

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Enji performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 04, 2024. 

Songs:
Zuud 00:00
Taivshral 04:43
Vogl 08:23
Zavkhan 12:40
Uzegdel 16:55

Enji (Enkhjargal Erkhembayar) - Vocals
Paul Braendle - Guitar
River Adomeit - Double Bass
Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Carlos Cruz
